Minimum Detectable Effect (MDE)

MDE is the minimum effect size required to acheive statistical significance. 

The difference between parameters of two groups 

The small difference you want to observe with statistical significance..

MDE is mostly setup based om ROI or some calculation..

MDE Range 

Low 1% - For large platforms..small change also makes lots or ROI.. facebook , uber

High 10% - For startups, if change is significantly enough..


For Netflix, MDE is 1%
